overview.en: Han Gong Assets uses real estate digitalization model to acquire real estate, solve construction, sales and management problems for real estate developers, and use the acquired assets as investors' base to ensure the safety of investment. Committed to building a world-class real estate digital trading platform for the global real estate industry economy and investors.
overview.zh: 汉宫资产通过房地产数字化模式，并购房地产，为房地产商解决建设,销售和管理问题，以并购的资产为投资者托底，确保投资的安全性。致力于为全球房地产产业经济，和广大投资者搭建一个全球顶尖级的房地产数字化交易平台。
